title: Free Rent! Stevens Sq 2BR 1bath 1 block to MCAD,  UMN
posting_body: ['Stevens Sq 2BR MCAD, walk to downtown, close to UMN & MCTC', 'Property Address', '1912 3rd Ave So.', '| 33 | Minneapolis, MN 55404', 'Available:', 'Aug 1st', 'Offered By', 'GISP, Inc.', '|', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'Check out this Stevens Sq 2 BR with a remodeled kitchen with breakfast bar.', ' The apartment has great light and new windows for maximum comfort.', 'We require a $45.00 application fee per adult when applying.', 'Income must be 2.0 x the rent.', ' No Evictions or UD’s convictions in the last 5 years.', 'No major credit accounts written off, delinquent, or in collections in last 5 years.', 'No felony convictions in the last five years or Misdemeanors in the last 3 years.', ' Those with felonies for murder, rape, arson, or assault will be denied.', 'No major lease violations from previous Landlord references.', 'We accept first time renters and co-signers.', 'We allow cats and dogs for an additional  pet rent and a one time $200.00 non refundable pet fee.', 'Units vary', 'This is a smoke free building.', 'Off-street parking is available for an additional fee.', 'For more information about our classic apartments and homes for rent or to apply on line go to <URL>', 'Amenities', 'One block to MCAD', 'On direct bus line to West Bank', '5 minute walk to downtown', 'close to MCC', 'Remodeled kitchen', 'hardwood floors', 'natural woodwork', 'on-line rent payment', 'on line maintenance requests', 'On site Laundry Facility', 'free storage', 'secured entry', 'Many shops nearby', '24 hour emergency service', 'Ceiling Fan', 'Common area and parking lot video surveillance', 'Free storage lockers', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 600', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $999.00', 'Available: 08/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $45.00', 'Security Deposit: $999.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
